<BaseLayout
  title="How Japanese B2B Buyers Evaluate Trust and Risk | Consilegy"
  description="A global technology company (approx. 120,000 employees) launched in Japan with strong global creative and generated almost no sales-ready pipeline. The problem was not the product. It was that the evaluation sequence Japan buyers follow was never addressed."
  lang="en"
  alternateUrl="/insights/"
>
